Olympic Legacy Committee Invites Bids for Two Media Centers

-- B y   R o s s   L a r s e n
-- 
2011-10-03T13:19:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/olympic-legacy-committee-invites-bids-for-two-media-centers.html
The Olympic Park Legacy Company
invited bids for the press center and broadcast center that will
be used during the 2012 games. Interested parties have nine
weeks to bid for the approximately one million square feet of
commercial space.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ross Larsen in London at 
